OL,5,CARE YOU HAVING TURKEY THIS CHRISTMAS?  
OL,7, If you were thinking of indulging in a 
OL,8, typical Christmas spread with the main 
OL,9, event being a breast of succulent      
OL,10, turkey, perhaps you shouldCthink twice.
OL,12, "Heart disease, mutilation, arthritis, 
OL,13, impotence, ulcers, obesity, stress,    
OL,14, salmonella...with sprouts and mash is  
OL,15, what you'll be chewing on," claims     
OL,16,CJuliet GellatleyGfromCViva.            
OL,18,CWhat does she mean? The Green Scene    
OL,19, endeavours to find out...              
