OL,5,CARE YOU HAVING TURKEY THIS CHRISTMAS?  
OL,7, OverC11 million turkeysGwill be killed 
OL,8, in the UK alone this Christmas, says   
OL,9, Juliet Gellatley from vegetarian       
OL,10, campaign group, Viva.                  
OL,12, "Tragically, most of these birds will  
OL,13, have beenCintensively-farmedGwith one  
OL,14, objective in mind - to make them as    
OL,15, big as possible in very little time.   
OL,17, "Indeed, some male birds, within four  
OL,18, months will be of the same weightCas an
OL,19,Ceight-year-old child."                 
