OL,5,CARE YOU HAVING TURKEY THIS CHRISTMAS?  
OL,7,C"Seed aloneGis not what makes turkeys  
OL,8, so big in such a short space of time," 
OL,9, claims Juliet Gellatley from Viva.     
OL,11, "They are fed onCgrowth promoting      
OL,12,CantibioticsGwhich make them grow twice 
OL,13, the size that they would under natural 
OL,14, conditions.                            
OL,16, "This causes all sorts of problems for 
OL,17, the birds fromCheart disease to        
OL,18,CarthritisGand who knows what effect the
OL,19, growth hormones will have on humans?"  
