OL,5,CARE YOU HAVING TURKEY THIS CHRISTMAS?  
OL,7, "Man-induced obesity in turkeys not    
OL,8, only causes the birds' bones to break, 
OL,9, it also prevents them fromCreproducing 
OL,10, naturally," says Juliet Gellatley from 
OL,11, Viva, the vegetarian campaign group.   
OL,13, "Farmers have toCmilk the malesG-Gthey 
OL,14, extract semen from male turkeys by hand
OL,15, and insert it into female birds.       
OL,17, "A lot of people laugh at this but it's
OL,18, no joke.CIt's painfulGand often leaves 
OL,19, the bird with a lot of bruising."      
