OL,5,CARE YOU HAVING TURKEY THIS CHRISTMAS?  
OL,7,C"Christmas is a time of goodwill,Gpeace
OL,8, on earth and forgiveness. Why celebrate
OL,9, it by cutting the throat of a pathetic,
OL,10, terrified creature?" asks Juliet       
OL,11, Gellatley from Viva.                   
OL,13, "This Christmas, we are calling on     
OL,14, people toCboycott turkey.GThere are so 
OL,15, many kinder, if not tastier,           
OL,16, alternatives."                         
OL,18,BGIf you're interested in alternative  
OL,19,   dishes contact Viva onC01273 777688. 
