OL,5,CARE YOU HAVING TURKEY THIS CHRISTMAS?  
OL,7, A spokeswoman fromCThe British Turkey  
OL,8,CFederationGsays the allegations made by
OL,9, Viva are "misleading".                 
OL,11, "UK turkeys areCreared to the highest  
OL,12,CstandardsGset out by the Government and
OL,13, independent bodies such as the Farm    
OL,14, Animal Welfare Council.                
OL,16, "It only makes sense for farmers to    
OL,17,Crear a healthy flockGwhich in turn they
OL,18, can sell on as prime-quality meat. If  
OL,19, you're having turkey, enjoy it!"       
